  "personalDirections": {
    "explanation": "Personal directions in Feng Shui are calculated based on a person's birth date according to the Chinese calendar. These personal directions can be used to determine favorable locations for different activities.",
    "kua": {
      "calculation": "To calculate your Kua Number: For men, subtract your birth year from 10. For women, add 5 to your birth year, then subtract from 10. If the result is 5, the Kua number is 5 for men and 8 for women. Always reduce double digits to a single digit except for 10, which becomes 1.",
